{
  "texts": [
    "LLMs can serve as reservoirs of knowledge.",
    "Although this is one of their more basic applications, it can be useful for PwD.",
    "Unlike conventional search engines that merely retrieve websites, LLMs excel in identifying, compiling and re-synthesizing knowledge and presenting it in an accessible and understandable form.",
    "Saeidnia et al. (2023) reported dementia caregivers were overall positive about the quality of answers given by ChatGPT to queries about non-clinical issues relevant to PwDs' lives.",
    "However, for questions related to dementia, LLMs may not be sufficiently accurate out of the box."
  ]
}